Output assets/rolecraft-demo.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 820
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set Framerate 12

Type "rolecraft install sametcelikbicak/task-decomposer --global"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 7000ms

Type "rolecraft list"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 5000ms

Type "clear"
Sleep 100ms
Enter
Sleep 1000ms

Type "rolecraft --help"
Sleep 200ms
Enter
Sleep 8000ms
